code: @Override protected Object createBody() {     try {         return endpoint.getHttpBinding().parseBody(this).     } catch (IOException e) {         throw new RuntimeCamelException(e).     } }
@Override public HttpMessage newInstance() {     return new HttpMessage(request, response, getExchange(), endpoint). }
@Override public String toString() {     // do not use toString on HTTP message     return "HttpMessage@" + ObjectHelper.getIdentityHashCode(this). }
